        <script type="text/jscript">
            // changes made on Dec 11
            // 1) merge the alert message to one
            // 2) change initialization for flag.   
            var acount = 0;
            var lengthcount = 0;
            var ok = "yes";
            var errorlist = "";
            var rr1 = 1;

            function countChoices() {
                if (rr1 == 0) {
                    errorlist = errorlist + 'Please select Yes or No.';
                    ok = "no";
                }
            }


            function validate(field) {

                var valid = "0123456789"
                var temp;
                for (var i = 0; i < field.value.length; i++) {
                    temp = "" + field.value.substring(i, i + 1);
                    lengthcount++;
                    if (valid.indexOf(temp) == "-1") ok = "no1";
                }
                if (ok == "yes") acount++;
            }


            function validate_all() {
                ret = false;
                acount = 0;
                ok = "yes";
                lengthcount = 0;
                errorlist = "";
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo1'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo2'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo3'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo4'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo5'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo6'));
                if ((acount == 6) && (lengthcount != 19)) { ok = "no"; errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
    if (ok == "no1") { errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
                if ((ok == "yes") && (lengthcount == 19)) countChoices();
                if (ok != "yes") alert(errorlist);
                if (ok == "yes") ret = true;

                return ret;
            }


        </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

        <script type="text/jscript">
            // changes made on Dec 11
            // 1) merge the alert message to one
            // 2) change initialization for flag.   
            var acount = 0;
            var lengthcount = 0;
            var ok = "yes";
            var errorlist = "";
            var rr1 = 1;

            function countChoices() {
                if (rr1 == 0) {
                    errorlist = errorlist + 'Please select Yes or No.';
                    ok = "no";
                }
            }


            function validate(field) {

                var valid = "0123456789"
                var temp;
                for (var i = 0; i < field.value.length; i++) {
                    temp = "" + field.value.substring(i, i + 1);
                    lengthcount++;
                    if (valid.indexOf(temp) == "-1") ok = "no1";
                }
                if (ok == "yes") acount++;
            }


            function validate_all() {
                ret = false;
                acount = 0;
                ok = "yes";
                lengthcount = 0;
                errorlist = "";
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo1'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo2'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo3'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo4'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo5'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo6'));
                if ((acount == 6) && (lengthcount != 19)) { ok = "no"; errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
    if (ok == "no1") { errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
                if ((ok == "yes") && (lengthcount == 19)) countChoices();
                if (ok != "yes") alert(errorlist);
                if (ok == "yes") ret = true;

                return ret;
            }


        </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">×</span></button>
              <div class="h4 modal-title" id="mdSessionLabel">Session Expiring</div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <p>Your e-File session will expire in:</p>
              <div class="progress">
                  <div id="prgSession" class="progress-bar progress-bar-danger" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 100%">
                  <span id="aboutVal"></span>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" onclick="extendSn();">Extend Session</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" name="ctl00$hdSessionLength" id="hdSessionLength" value="60" />
      <input type="hidden" name="ctl00$hdSessionAboutTo" id="hdSessionAboutTo" value="5" />
      <span style="display:none;">
          <input type="submit" name="ctl00$ctl12" value="OK" />
      </span>
    </form>
    
    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("table").prepend("<caption>Data Table</caption>");
        $("table.calendarTitleExt tbody").prepend("<tr><th scope='col' style='display:none;'>Month</th></tr>");
    });
    </script>

      <div class="modal fade" id="mdSession" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mdSessionLabel">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header bg-warning">
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">×</span></button>
              <div class="h4 modal-title" id="mdSessionLabel">Session Expiring</div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <p>Your e-File session will expire in:</p>
              <div class="progress">
                  <div id="prgSession" class="progress-bar progress-bar-danger" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 100%">
                  <span id="aboutVal"></span>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" onclick="extendSn();">Extend Session</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" name="ctl00$hdSessionLength" id="hdSessionLength" value="60" />
      <input type="hidden" name="ctl00$hdSessionAboutTo" id="hdSessionAboutTo" value="5" />
      <span style="display:none;">
          <input type="submit" name="ctl00$ctl12" value="OK" />
      </span>
    </form>
    
    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("table").prepend("<caption>Data Table</caption>");
        $("table.calendarTitleExt tbody").prepend("<tr><th scope='col' style='display:none;'>Month</th></tr>");
    });
    </script>

        <script type="text/jscript">
            // changes made on Dec 11
            // 1) merge the alert message to one
            // 2) change initialization for flag.   
            var acount = 0;
            var lengthcount = 0;
            var ok = "yes";
            var errorlist = "";
            var rr1 = 1;

            function countChoices() {
                if (rr1 == 0) {
                    errorlist = errorlist + 'Please select Yes or No.';
                    ok = "no";
                }
            }


            function validate(field) {

                var valid = "0123456789"
                var temp;
                for (var i = 0; i < field.value.length; i++) {
                    temp = "" + field.value.substring(i, i + 1);
                    lengthcount++;
                    if (valid.indexOf(temp) == "-1") ok = "no1";
                }
                if (ok == "yes") acount++;
            }


            function validate_all() {
                ret = false;
                acount = 0;
                ok = "yes";
                lengthcount = 0;
                errorlist = "";
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo1'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo2'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo3'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo4'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo5'));
                validate(document.getElementById('MainContent_txtRollNo6'));
                if ((acount == 6) && (lengthcount != 19)) { ok = "no"; errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
    if (ok == "no1") { errorlist = errorlist + 'Please ensure the Roll Number is entered properly.\n'; }
                if ((ok == "yes") && (lengthcount == 19)) countChoices();
                if (ok != "yes") alert(errorlist);
                if (ok == "yes") ret = true;

                return ret;
            }


        </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">

    var dtLd = new Date();
    var mdSn = false;
    var ssA = parseInt($('#hdSessionAboutTo').val());

    var mInt;
    if (window.location.href.indexOf("SessionExpired") < 0) {
        mInt = setInterval(checkSn, 20000);
    }

    function checkSn() {
        var dtNw = new Date();
        var dtChA = new Date(dtLd.toString());
        var dtChE = new Date(dtLd.toString());

        var ssL = parseInt($('#hdSessionLength').val());

        dtChA.setMinutes(dtChA.getMinutes() + ssL - ssA);
        dtChE.setMinutes(dtChE.getMinutes() + ssL);

        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChA.valueOf()) {
            if (!mdSn) {
                showSsnMd();
            }
            mdSn = true;
            
        }
        if (dtNw.valueOf() > dtChE.valueOf()) {
            clearInterval(mInt);
            window.location = "SessionExpired.aspx";
        }
    }

    function extendSn() {
        dtLd = new Date();
        mdSn = false;
        $('#mdSession').modal('hide');

        $.ajax({
            url: "About.aspx",
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            success: function (result) {
            },
            error: function (xhr) {
            }
        });
    }

    var wdNw;
    var ssASec;
    var mIntP;
    function showSsnMd() {
        $('#aboutVal').html(ssA + ':00');
        $('#mdSession').modal('show');

        wdNw = 100;
        ssASec = ssA * 60;
        mIntP = setInterval(showProgress, 1000);
    }
                    
    function showProgress() {
        ssASec--;
        if (ssASec >= 0) {
            var d = new Date(ssASec * 1000);
            var mm = d.getMinutes();
            var ss = d.getSeconds();
            if (ss < 10) { ss = '0' + ss; }

            var pr = parseInt((ssASec * 100) / (ssA * 60));
            $('#prgSession').attr('aria-valuenow', pr).css('width', pr + '%');
            $('#aboutVal').html(mm + ':' + ss);
        }
        if (ssASec <= 0) {
            clearInterval(mIntP);
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("table").prepend("<caption>Data Table</caption>");
        $("table.calendarTitleExt tbody").prepend("<tr><th scope='col' style='display:none;'>Month</th></tr>");
    });
